Class EDIFPortInstList

  • Object
    • AbstractCollection<E>
      • AbstractList<E>
        • ArrayList<EDIFPortInst>
          • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.EDIFPortInstList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<EDIFPortInst>, Collection<EDIFPortInst>, List<EDIFPortInst>, RandomAccess

    public class EDIFPortInstList
extends ArrayList<EDIFPortInst>
    Customized ArrayList for the EDIFNet and EDIFCellInst classes. Maintains a sorted list to allow for a O(log n) retrieval lookup by name. Overwrites existing entries with most recent value.
    See Also:

        public boolean add(EDIFPortInst e)
        Inserts the port inst into the list such that the list remains sorted. If an identical element is already in the list, it is overwritten with the new port instance provided.

        public void deferSortAdd(EDIFPortInst e)
